text.tspan: Fertilizer use vs. GDP per capita, 2022
Average fertilizer use, measured in kilograms per hectare of cropland versus GDP per capita, adjusted for
inflation and for differences in living costs between countries.
Data source: Food and Agriculture Organization of the United Nations (2025); Eurostat, OECD, and World Bank (2025)

Note: GDP per capita is expressed in
international-$
at 2021 prices.
